sky%20is%20cloudy%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6893bc823d5881a51c1ebe52%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222607%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFort%20Stewart%20is%20home%20to%20the%20US%20Army's%203rd%20Infantry%20Division%20and%20Hunter%20Army%20Airfield.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FRuss%20Bynum%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EUS%20Army%20officials%20shared%20details%20on%20the%20shooting%20at%20Fort%20Stewart%2C%20Georgia%2C%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFive%20soldiers%20were%20shot%20in%20the%202nd%20Armored%20Brigade%20Combat%20area%20of%20the%20base.%20The%20victims%20are%20in%20stable%20condition.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Army%20identified%20the%20shooting%20suspect%20as%20Sgt.%20Quornelius%20Radford.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20US%20Army%20general%20said%20Thursday%20afternoon%20that%20the%20shooting%20at%20Fort%20Stewart%20in%20Georgia%20earlier%20in%20the%20day%20involved%20a%20soldier%20with%20a%20personal%20handgun%20and%20his%20coworkers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArmy%20officials%20identified%20the%20shooting%20suspect%20as%2028-year-old%20Sgt.%20Quornelius%20Radford%2C%20who%20is%20now%20in%20custody%20and%20being%20questioned%20by%20the%20Army%20Criminal%20Investigation%20Division.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shooting%20occurred%20Wednesday%20morning%20at%20the%202nd%20Armored%20Brigade%20Combat%20area%20of%20the%20base.%20Radford%2C%20officials%20alleged%2C%20brought%20his%20personal%20handgun%20onto%20base%20and%20shot%20five%20people%20before%20being%20subdued%20and%20subsequently%20apprehended.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrig.%20Gen.%20John%20Lubas%2C%20the%20commanding%20general%20for%20the%203rd%20Infantry%20Division%2C%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dvidshub.net%2Fwebcast%2F36623%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epress%20conference%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20all%20of%20the%20victims%20are%20currently%20in%20stable%20condition%20at%20a%20nearby%20hospital%20and%20their%20families%20have%20been%20notified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20motivations%20for%20the%20shooting%20are%20currently%20unknown%2C%20Lubas%20shared%20that%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20we%20know%20is%20the%20soldier%2C%20the%20shooting%20occurred%20at%20the%20soldier's%20place%20of%20work.%20It%20did%20involve%20his%20coworkers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226584%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Five%20soldiers%20walk%20in%20a%20line%20on%20pavement%20with%20grass%2C%20trees%2C%20and%20a%20building%20in%20the%20background.%20The%20sky%20is%20blue%20with%20some%20clouds.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6893bce0f748d8c055f70597%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223704%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELubas%20said%20Army%20officials%20were%20determining%20how%20the%20suspect%20got%20his%20handgun%20on%20base.%3Cp%3EUS%20Army%20photo%20by%20Pfc.%20Jude%20Vogel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20soldiers%20in%20the%20area%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20incident%20%26quot%3Bimmediately%20and%20without%20hesitation%20tackled%26quot%3B%20the%20shooting%20suspect%2C%20subduing%20him%20before%20law%20enforcement%20took%20him%20into%20custody%2C%20Lubas%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20Wednesday%20afternoon%20press%20conference%2C%20Lubas%20said%20that%20he%20was%20unaware%20of%20any%20behavioral%20issues%20involving%20the%20shooting%20suspect%20and%20confirmed%20that%20they%20did%20not%20use%20a%20military%20weapon.%20%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20it%20was%20a%20personal%20handgun%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20Lubas%20said%20it%20was%20unclear%20how%20the%20shooting%20suspect%20got%20the%20handgun%20on%20base.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERadford%2C%20Lubas%20said%2C%20had%20been%20arrested%20on%20charges%20of%20driving%20under%20the%20influence%20in%20May.%20His%20chain%20of%20command%20was%20unaware%20of%20these%20charges%20prior%20to%20the%20shooting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shooting%20is%20the%20latest%20in%20a%20string%20of%20violent%20incidents%20at%20US%20military%20bases%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20some%20described%20by%20law%20enforcement%20and%20military%20officials%20as%20workplace%20shootings%20and%20others%20as%20acts%20of%20terrorism.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20previous%20incident%20in%20December%202022%20in%20which%20a%20soldier%20shot%20and%20killed%20a%20sergeant%20at%20Fort%20Stewart.%20The%20shooter%20used%20a%20personal%20handgun%20and%20was%20charged%20with%20murder%20in%20military%20court.%20Both%20the%20shooter%20and%20victim%20served%20in%20the%202nd%20Brigade%20Combat%20Team%20of%20the%203rd%20Infantry%20Division.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffort-stewart-shooting-shooter-sergeant-quornelius-radford-2025-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1754514270000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6893bd30194a2d49b8ae1f4e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffort-stewart-shooting-shooter-sergeant-quornelius-radford-2025-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Fort%20Stewart%20shooting%20suspect%20was%20identified%20as%2028-year-old%20Sgt.%20Quornelius%20Radford.%20Five%20people%20were%20wounded%20in%20the%20incident.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cpanella%40businessinsider.com%20(Chris%20Panella)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A30%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffort-stewart-shooting-shooter-sergeant-quornelius-radford-2025-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Alison%20Pill%20Signs%20with%20Gersh%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1754514040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FAlison21656-150-e1754511888376.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236480974%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22