rl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rate%20cuts%20could%20be%20weeks%20away.%20Here's%20how%20much%20history%20says%20stocks%20could%20rise%20as%20the%20Fed%20eases%20policy.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22traders%20celebrating%20soccer%20world%20cup%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5b1ff66d1ae66237008b5849%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221423%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ERichard%20Drew%2FAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EInvestors%20expect%20the%20Fed%20to%20resume%20rate%20cuts%20next%20month.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHistorically%2C%20rate%20cuts%20have%20led%20to%20strong%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20gains%2C%20but%20there%20have%20been%20exceptions.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHere's%20what%20history%20says%20about%20how%20the%20market%20behaves%20once%20rate%20cuts%20start%20back%20up.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjuly-jobs-report-unemployment-rate-employment-federal-reserve-interest-rates-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eweak%20few%20months%20of%20job%20growth%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20investors%20are%20banking%20on%20rate%20cuts%20from%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20at%20their%20September%20meeting%2C%20and%20history%20shows%20cuts%20could%20be%20like%20rocket%20fuel%20for%20stocks%20in%20the%20months%20that%20follow.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELPL%20Financial%20recently%20conducted%20an%20analysis%20of%20how%20stocks%20have%20performed%20from%20the%20first%20rate%20cut%20in%20a%20rate-reduction%20cycle%20until%20the%20eventual%20start%20of%20a%20new%20hiking%20cycle.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20average%2C%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20has%20returned%2030.3%25%20during%20the%20nine%20periods%20when%20rates%20have%20been%20on%20the%20decline%20since%201974.%20The%20median%20return%20during%20those%20periods%20was%2013.3%25.%20Returns%20have%20been%20positive%20in%20six%20of%20those%20nine%20cycles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUsing%20history%20and%20prior%20Fed%20cutting%20cycles%20as%20a%20guide%2C%20some%20upside%20potential%20may%20remain%20for%20the%20second%20half%20of%202025%2C%26quot%3B%20Jeff%20Buchbinder%2C%20LPL's%20chief%20equity%20strategist%2C%20said%20in%20the%20August%205%20report.%20%26quot%3BBut%20of%20course%2C%20past%20performance%20does%20not%20guarantee%20future%20results%2C%20and%20a%20new%20tariff%20regime%20not%20seen%20since%20the%201930s%20could%20slow%20earnings%20growth%20and%20fuel%20volatility.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20largest%20market%20surges%20came%20in%20the%20lead%20up%20to%20the%20dot-com%20bubble%2C%20when%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20rose%20161%25%20from%201995%20to%201999%2C%20the%20analysis%20showed.%20Other%20big%20gains%20included%2062.8%25%20from%201984%20to%201993%2C%20and%2038.2%25%20from%202019%20to%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20rate%20cuts%20aren't%20always%20a%20tailwind%2C%20especially%20during%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finterest-rate-cuts-federal-reserve-economy-recession-soft-landing-powell-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erecessionary%20periods%20where%20the%20Fed%20acts%20too%20late%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20market%20fell%2023.5%25%20during%20the%202007-2009%20rate-cutting%20cycle%2C%20and%20from%202001-2004%2C%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20dropped%209.6%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20time%20around%2C%20Buchbinder%20said%20it's%20not%20a%20sure%20thing%20that%20rate%20cuts%20will%20be%20a%20boon%20for%20stocks%2C%20with%20ebullient%20investor%20sentiment%20having%20pushed%20up%20the%20market%20to%20new%20highs%20despite%20uncertainty%20remaining%20about%20the%20health%20of%20the%20economy.%20The%20market%20has%20also%20risen%2012%25%20already%20since%20the%20Fed's%20first%20cut%20of%20the%20cycle%20last%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20delayed%20effects%20of%20trade%20policy%20are%20likely%20to%20weigh%20on%20the%20economy%20in%20the%20second%20half%2C%20leading%20to%20weaker%20labor%20market%20demand%2C%26quot%3B%20Buchbinder%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BRecent%20market%20complacency%20toward%20trade%20policy%20and%20an%20economic%20narrative%20dependent%20upon%20strong%20economic%20data%20has%20caught%20our%20attention%20in%20recent%20weeks%20as%20a%20potential%20point%20of%20weakness.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20not%20a%20guarantee%20the%20Fed%20continues%20to%20ease%20policy%20in%20the%20months%20ahead.%20Economists%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffed-interest-rate-cuts-powell-jobs-report-bofa-morgan-stanely-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMorgan%20Stanley%20and%20Bank%20of%20America%3C%2Fa%3E%20both%20see%20the%20central%20bank%20keeping%20rates%20steady%20for%20the%20rest%20of%202025%20despite%20CME%20FedWatch%20data%20showing%20investors%20pricing%20in%2093.2%25%20odds%20that%20the%20Fed%20cuts%20in%20next%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20apparent%20heightened%20levels%20of%20risk%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20Buchbinder%20said%20a%20conservative%20approach%20could%20be%20the%20best%20way%20forward%20in%20the%20near%20term.%20The%20firm%20likes%20growth%20stocks%2C%20large%20caps%2C%20and%20the%20financials%20and%20communication%20services%20sectors%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBottom%20line%2C%20investors%20may%20be%20well%20served%20by%20bracing%20for%20occasional%20bouts%20of%20volatility%20given%20how%20much%20optimism%20is%20currently%20reflected%20in%20equity%20prices%2C%26quot%3B%20Buchbinder%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm's%20short-term%20asset%20allocation%20committee%20%26quot%3Badvises%20against%20increasing%20portfolio%20risk%20beyond%20benchmark%20targets%20currently%20and%20continues%20to%20monitor%20tariff%20negotiations%2C%20economic%20data%2C%20earnings%2C%20the%20bond%20market%2C%20and%20various%20technical%20indicators%20to%20identify%20a%20potentially%20more%20attractive%20entry%20point%20to%20add%20equities%20on%20weakness%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffed-rate-cuts-stock-market-performance-sp500-gains-economy-inflation-2025-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1754505381000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F642dd2bfde7d9200193a2fdd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffed-rate-cuts-stock-market-performance-sp500-gains-economy-inflation-2025-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Markets%20are%20feeling%20confident%20the%20Fed%20will%20cut%20rates%20next%20month.%20History%20shows%20how%20that%20could%20be%20rocket%20fuel%20for%20stocks.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22wedwards%40businessinsider.com%20(William%20Edwards)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffed-rate-cuts-stock-market-performance-sp500-gains-economy-inflation-2025-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'I%20could%20not%20protect%20her'%3A%20Mother%20says%20her%20six-year-old%20daughter%20was%20told%20to%20'go%20back%20to%20India'%3B%20bicycle%20wheel%20was%20pushed%20onto%20her%20private%20parts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1754505276000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-123149263%2Cimgsize-61568.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fi-could-not-protect-her-mother-says-her-six-year-old-daughter-was-told-to-go-back-to-india-bicycle-wheel-was-pushed-onto-her-private-parts%2Farticleshow%2F123149123.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F123149123.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2F