ld.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EEverything%20fit%20with%20room%20to%20spare%3A%20Full-sized%20shampoo%20bottles%2C%20electric%20razors%2C%20bulky%20prescription%20containers.%20While%20it%20doesn't%20offer%20the%20same%20fine-tuned%20organizational%20options%20as%20other%20models%2C%20the%20Nido's%20focus%20on%20raw%20capacity%20makes%20it%20an%20excellent%20choice%20for%20anyone%20with%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20products%20or%20who%20wants%20to%20share%20a%20bag%20with%20their%20travel%20partner.%20The%20layout%20itself%20is%20simple%20but%20effective%2C%20featuring%20one%20large%20main%20compartment%20and%20two%20slightly%20smaller%20side%20pockets%20%E2%80%94%20each%20with%20its%20own%20zipper%20%E2%80%94%20providing%20useful%20separation%20without%20overcomplicating%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIts%20bright%2C%20bold%20aesthetic%20sets%20it%20apart%20from%20other%20bags.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThis%20not%20only%20makes%20it%20easier%20to%20see%20items%20inside%20(thanks%20to%20the%20bright%20interior%20colors)%2C%20but%20also%20prevents%20the%20bag%20from%20getting%20mixed%20up%20with%20other%20ones%20on%20a%20group%20trip.%20This%20multi-colored%20design%20isn't%20just%20eye-catching%2C%20it's%20also%20made%20with%20seriously%20high-quality%20materials.%20The%20840D%20nylon%20exterior%20and%20630D%20side%20panels%20feel%20extremely%20sturdy%20and%20durable%2C%20and%20easily%20held%20up%20during%20my%20durability%20tests%20(and%20most%20likely%20the%20wear%20and%20tear%20of%20regular%20travel).%20Despite%20its%204-liter%20capacity%20(one%20of%20the%20most%20spacious%20options%20I%20tested)%2C%20at%20just%206.5%20ounces%2C%20it%20doesn't%20add%20unnecessary%20weight%20to%20your%20luggage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMinimalist%20packers%20might%20find%20the%20Nido%20a%20bit%20oversized%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20but%20for%20those%20who%20travel%20with%20a%20full%20suite%20of%20grooming%20products%20%E2%80%94%20or%20just%20like%20having%20a%20lot%20of%20options%20on%20hand%20%E2%