tic%20zipper%20pulls)%2C%20and%20the%20reinforced%20grab%20handle%20is%20large%20enough%20to%20grip%20and%20carry%20easily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Osprey%20Daylite%20Toiletry%20Kit%20lacks%20the%20bells%20and%20whistles%20of%20higher-end%20models%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20but%20its%20reliable%20construction%20and%20roomy%20interior%20still%20make%20it%20a%20smart%20buy%20for%20value-minded%20travelers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a2180544-8dcc-48ed-9a49-83d623263ac1%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20hanging%5C%22%3EBest%20hanging%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20prefer%20to%20hang%20your%20toiletry%20bag%20for%20easier%20access%20%E2%80%94%20a%20practice%20I've%20found%20to%20be%20especially%20useful%20in%20hotel%20bathrooms%20or%20shared%20spaces%20%E2%80%94%20this%20July%20model%20was%20the%20best%20option%20I%20tested.%20Designed%20with%20convenience%20and%20functionality%20in%20mind%2C%20this%20bag%20combines%20a%20spacious%20interior%20layout%20with%20thoughtful%20organization%2C%20all%20in%20a%20lightweight%20and%20travel-friendly%20package.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20was%20impressed%20with%20just%20how%20much%20stuff%20this%20bag%20could%20hold.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Among%20the%20other%20hanging%20kits%20I%20tested%2C%20its%204.2-liter%20capacity%20ranked%20the%20best%20in%20terms%20of%20overall%20storage%20space%2C%20and%20its%20multiple%20compartments%20strike%20a%20useful%20balance%20of%20structure%20and%20accessibility.%20Regardless%20of%20the%20type%20and%20size%20of%20items%20you're%20packing%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20that's%20skincare%20products%2C%20grooming%20tools%2C%20or%20travel-sized%20bottles%20%E2%80%94%20everything%20has%20its%20own%2C%20secure%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20cream-colored%20toiletry%20bag%20is%20open%20on%20a%20dark%20wooden%20surface%2C%20revealing%20neatly%20packed%20travel%20essentials.%20The%20left%20compartment%20holds%20full-sized%20shampoo%2C%20conditioner%2C%20body%20wash%2C%20and%20a%20tube%20of%20Colgate%20toothpaste%20inside%20a%20clear%20zippered%20section.%20The%20center%20has%20a%20loop%20holding%20smaller%20items%20like%20sunscreen%2C%20lotion%2C%20and%20a%20face%20mask%20packet.%20The%20right%20zippered%20pocket%20contains%20tins%20and%20jars%2C%20possibly%20for%20skincare%20or%20balms.%20A%20metal%20hook%20for%20hanging%20the%20bag%20is%20visible%20on%20the%20left%20side.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68924ab585e81483682f52f2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIf%20you%20frequently%20stay%20in%20hotels%20or%20find%20yourself%20navigating%20shared%20bathrooms%20on%20the%20road%2C%20the%20July%20Hanging%20Toiletry%20Bag%20offers%20a%20really%20useful%20mix%20of%20space%2C%20structure%2C%20and%20hanging%20versatility.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Rennie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOne%20of%20my%20favorite%20features%20of%20this%20bag%20is%20the%20sturdy%20metal%20hanging%20hook%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20which%20not%20only%20tucks%20neatly%20away%20when%20not%20in%20use%2C%20but%20adds%20a%20level%20of%20durability%20and%20a%20high-end%20%26quot%3Bpolished%26quot%3B%20look.%20Many%20hanging%20kits%20rely%20on%20plastic%20or%20flimsy%20fabric%20loops%2C%20but%20this%20hook%20(and%20its%20connection%20to%20the%20bag)%20really%20feels%20like%20it%20can%20handle%20the%20weight%20of%20a%20full%20bag%20without%20stress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDespite%20its%20impressive%20capacity%2C%20the%20July%20bag%20is%20still%20really%20easy%20to%20pack%20up%20and%20carry.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20lightweight%20nylon%20construction%20keeps%20everything%20feeling%20sleek%20yet%20sturdy%2C%20and%20the%20subtle%20color%20options%20make%20it%20a%20bit%20more%20refined%20than%20the%20typical%20utilitarian-style%20I%20see%20used%20by%20most%20toiletry%20bags.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22417e7edb-6c04-49e3-bfad-b908e230c554%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20small%5C%22%3EBest%20small%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThis%20versatile%20bag%20packs%20a%20ton%20of%20storage%20options%20and%20features%20into%20a%20rectangular%2C%20easy-to-pack%20shape.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EDespite%20its%20compact%202.5-liter%20size%2C%20the%20Aer%20Travel%20Kit%202%20Ultra%20delivers%20a%20level%20of%20organization%20and%20adaptability%20I%20typically%20only%20find%20in%20much%20larger%2C%20bulkier%20options.%20The%20interior%20provides%20a%20ton%20of%20useful%20storage%20features%20such%20as%20elastic%20loops%20for%20bottles%2C%20a%20mesh%20zippered%20pocket%2C%20and%20dedicated%20toothbrush%20holders%2C%20all%20thoughtfully%20arranged%20to%20keep%20your%20items%20secure%20and%20accessible.%20On%20the%20outside%2C%20dual%20zippered%20pockets%20provide%20additional%20quick-access%20storage%20for%20items%20like%20a%20razor%2C%20travel%20wipes%2C%20or%20a%20contact%20lens%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20aer%20toiletry%20bag%20packed%20with%20small%20travel%20sized%20bottles%2C%20sitting%20on%20a%20towel%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6893544bf748d8c055f6f7ee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20bag's%20bright%20interior%20makes%20it%20easy%20to%20see%20what's%20inside%2C%20even%20in%20dimly%20lit%20showers%20or%20bathrooms.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Rennie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20I%20really%20appreciated%20about%20this%20bag%20was%20its%20attention%20to%20overall%20usability.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20bright%20interior%20lining%20dramatically%20improves%20visibility%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20helpful%20when%20rummaging%20around%20in%20a%20dim%20hotel%20room%20or%20camping%20tent%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20built-in%20hanging%20hook%20disappears%20into%20a%20hidden%20pocket%20for%20added%20functionality.%20The%20rectangular%20shape%20was%20another%20standout%20feature%2C%20making%20it%20easy%20to%20slide%20into%20a%20packed%20suitcase%20or%20weekender%20bag%20without%20wasting%20space.%20If%20you%20want%20a%20multifunctional%20toiletry%20bag%20that%20stays%20organized%2C%20travels%20well%2C%20and%20adapts%20to%20your%20packing%20style%2C%20this%20is%20one%20of%20the%20smartest%20designs%20out%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2278764bd4-5ac5-42d7-a74a-5eb3457d4fbd%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20camping%5C%22%3EBest%20for%20camping%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20REI%20Co-op%20Travel%20Kit's%20ultralight%202.8-ounce%20weight%20makes%20it%20particularly%20well-suited%20to%20camping%20and%20hiking%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20adding%20minimal%20heft%20and%20bulk%20to%20your%20pack.%20Despite%20the%20featherweight%20build%2C%20it%20proved%20surprisingly%20rugged%20during%20my%20durability%20tests%2C%20holding%20up%20well%20to%20rough%20handling%20and%20aggressive%20yanks%2C%20tugs%2C%20and%20scuffs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20bag's%20layout%20is%20straightforward%20but%20also%20well%20thought%20out.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Its%20multifunctional%20hanging%20strap%20makes%20it%20easy%20to%20hang%20from%20a%20tree%20branch%2C%20tent%20pole%2C%20or%20shared%20bathroom%20hook.%20That%20flexibility%20makes%20it%20far%20more%20useful%20in%20unpredictable%20outdoor%20setups%20where%20counter%20space%20may%20be%20nonexistent.%20Inside%2C%20it%20offers%20room%20for%20the%20basics%2C%20with%20just%20enough%20structure%20to%20keep%20things%20in%20place%20without%20overcomplicating%20design.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222675%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22close%20up%20of%20the%20strap%20of%20the%20rei%20travel%20bag%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68938f9f3d5881a51c1eb82f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222006%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20bag's%20adjustable%20strap%20lets%20you%20secure%20the%20bag%20to%20a%20pack%20for%20more%20secure%20carrying.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Rennie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20really%20impressed%20me%20about%20this%20bag%20was%20its%20impressive%20durability%20for%20the%20price.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAt%20just%20around%20%2420%2C%20the%20REI%20Co-op%20Travel%20Kit%20punches%20well%20above%20its%20weight%20class%2C%20using%20quality%20materials%2C%20smooth%20zippers%2C%20and%20a%20simple%2C%20functional%20layout.%20If%20you're%20planning%20a%20hiking%20trip%2C%20camping%20weekend%2C%20or%20just%20want%20something%20lightweight%20and%20tough%2C%20this%20bag%20is%20a%20fantastic%20no-frills%20option.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2225b63190-a787-4c65-8805-c0df46076344%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20test%20toiletry%20bags%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EHow%20we%20test%20toiletry%20bags%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20objectively%20evaluate%20all%20the%20bags%20in%20my%20testing%20pool%2C%20I%20created%20and%20utilized%20a%20structured%20testing%20rubric%2C%20assigning%20scores%20for%20each%20of%20my%20primary%20and%20secondary%20evaluation%20points.%20This%20comprehensive%20process%20involved%20hands-on%20testing%20of%2010%20toiletry%20bags%20over%20the%20course%20of%20a%20month.%20Here's%20what%20I%20looked%20for%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EUsability%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20first%20used%20each%20bag%20to%20store%20a%20variety%20of%20items%2C%20including%20different%20types%20and%20sizes%20of%20toiletry%20items%2C%20in%20order%20to%20fully%20use%20the%20available%20storage%20and%20any%20organizational%20features.%20I%20assessed%20the%20usability%20of%20any%20opening%20and%20closing%20mechanisms%2C%20noting%20whether%20zippers%20were%20smooth%20or%20frustrating%20to%20operate.%20I%20also%20evaluated%20if%20the%20bag's%20opening%20was%20large%20enough%20for%20easy%20access%20to%20the%20interior%2C%20and%20if%20the%20organizational%20elements%20allowed%20for%20convenient%20packing%20and%20removal%20of%20items.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EOrganization%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20also%20evaluated%20if%20each%20bag%20provided%20sufficient%20organizational%20pockets%2C%20sleeves%2C%20or%20compartments%20to%20neatly%20arrange%20items%2C%20without%20being%20overwhelming%20or%20inconvenient%20to%20navigate.%20I%20noted%20whether%20these%20elements%20came%20in%20a%20range%20of%20sizes%20and%20shapes%20to%20accommodate%20different%20types%20of%20items%20and%20devices.%20To%20effectively%20test%20how%20well%20these%20items%20stayed%20in%20place%2C%20I%20shook%20each%20full%20bag%20vigorously%20for%2020%20seconds%2C%20and%20then%20checked%20if%20items%20had%20become%20dislodged%20or%20spilled%20out%20of%20their%20designated%20areas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ECapacity%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhile%20bigger%20isn't%20always%20better%2C%20I%20felt%20it%20was%20important%20to%20determine%20if%20each%20bag%20was%20large%20enough%20to%20meet%20typical%20toiletry%20needs.%20This%20involved%20comparing%20the%20stated%20capacity%20(which%20ranged%20from%202.5%20to%204.2%20liters)%20with%20the%20functional%20capacity%20and%20evaluating%20how%20effectively%20the%20design%20accommodated%20various%20items.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EDurability%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETo%20assess%20build%20quality%20and%20long-term%20durability%2C%20I%20subjected%20each%20bag%20to%20aggressive%20handling%20tests%2C%20which%20included%20tugging%2C%20yanking%2C%20and%20pulling%20on%20zippers%2C%20straps%2C%20and%20pockets.%20I%20noted%20whether%20the%20stitching%20and%20fabric%20felt%20strong%20and%20secure%2C%20or%20felt%20cheap%2C%20flimsy%2C%20or%20prone%20to%20breakage.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ELeakproofness%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETo%20evaluate%20the%20leak%20resistance%20of%20each%20bag%20and%20determine%20how%20well%20it%20could%20contain%20any%20potential%20spills%20(important%20for%20protecting%20your%20other%20luggage%20if%20stored%20in%20a%20bag)%2C%20I%20filled%20each%20bag%20with%20%C2%BD%20cup%20of%20water%20and%20turned%20it%20upside%20down.%20I%20observed%20whether%20the%20bag%20successfully%20contained%20the%20liquid%20or%20if%20it%20leaked%20through%20the%20zipper%20or%20other%20openings.%20I%20think%20it's%20important%20to%20note%20that%20none%20of%20the%20bags%20I%20tested%20were%20100%25%20waterproof%2C%20but%20some%20zippers%20and%20rubber%20zipper%20covers%20did%20a%20better%20job%20than%20others%20of%20containing%20the%20leaks.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EPortability%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20also%20evaluated%20each%20bag's%20overall%20portability%20based%20on%20whether%20it%20was%20lightweight%20and%20compact%20enough%20for%20easy%20transport%20or%20if%20it%20felt%20noticeably%20heavier%20and%20bulkier.%20Factors%20such%20as%20actual%20weight%20(which%20ranged%20from%202.8%20to%208.8%20ounces)%2C%20dimensions%2C%20shape%2C%20and%20design%20elements%20like%20carabiners%2C%20hooks%2C%20straps%2C%20and%20handles%20that%20offered%20additional%20carrying%20options%20were%20also%20considered.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ECleaning%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EFinally%2C%20I%20compared%20how%20easy%20it%20was%20to%20clean%20each%20bag%20after%20use.%20This%20test%20involved%20squeezing%20toothpaste%20and%20shampoo%20into%20the%20bag%20and%20then%20cleaning%20it%20according%20to%20the%20provided%20instructions.%20I%20noted%20how%20convenient%20this%20process%20was%2C%20whether%20there%20were%20hard-to-reach%20nooks%20and%20crannies%2C%20and%20how%20quickly%20the%20bag%20dried%20after%20cleaning%20(typically%20monitoring%20dampness%20after%2030%20minutes).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229b450734-2901-4f6e-af7a-ae12e4a569d4%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20else%20we%20tested%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat