india.com%2F301742%2Fkerala-businessman-turns-barren-mining-land-into-bamboo-miyawaki-forest%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeco-conscious%20homeowners%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20resorts%2C%20and%20farmhouses%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20natural%20swimming%20pond%20takes%20around%2045%20days%20to%20build%20and%20can%20be%20customised%20to%20include%20koi%20ponds%2C%20waterfalls%2C%20and%20even%20meandering%20natural%20streams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pools%20require%20almost%20no%20maintenance%2C%20use%20no%20concrete%20or%20plastic%20linings%2C%20and%20support%20local%20biodiversity.%20Vikash%E2%80%99s%20approach%20not%20only%20rethinks%20luxury%20but%20redefines%20sustainability%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20in%20a%20water-scarce%20country%20like%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20venture%20now%20earns%20over%20Rs%203%20crore%20annually%2C%20but%20what%20he%20values%20most%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20revenue%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20ripple%20effect.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20come%20to%20me%20not%20just%20for%20a%20pool%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3E30Stades%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthey%20come%20for%20a%20piece%20of%20nature%20they%20thought%20was%20lost.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20more%20Indians%20seek%20green%20alternatives%20and%20reconnect%20with%20the%20natural%20world%2C%20Vikash%E2%80%99s%20story%20is%20a%20reminder%20that%20the%20best%20innovations%20are%20often%20rooted%20in%20the%20simplest%20childhood%20memories.%20Sometimes%2C%20going%20back%20to%20the%20pond%20is%20how%20you%20move%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1754312400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-31T161854.799-1753959023.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D479099%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20Coimbatore-based%20chartered%20accountant%20Vikash%20Kumar%20went%20looking%20for%20a%20chemical-free%20swimming%20pool%20for%20his%20young%20son%2C%20he%20realised%20that%20most%20city%20pools%20were%20loaded%20with%20chlorine%20%E2%80%94%20harsh%20on%20the%20skin%2C%20hair%2C%20and%20even%20the%20lungs.%20Drawing%20inspiration%20from%20the%20natural%20village%20ponds%20of%20his%20childhood%2C%20Vikash%20decided%20to%20build%20a%20swimming%20pool%20using%20nothing%20but%20natural%20materials%20%E2%80%94%20no%20cement%2C%20no%20chemicals.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Srimoyee%20Chowdhury%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F479099%2Fca-chemical-free-swimming-pools-biosphere-coimbatore%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Escape%20City%20Life%20in%20This%20Fairytale%20Mud%20Home%20in%20Rishikesh%2C%20Built%20by%2090%20People%20From%2018%20Countries%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFeatured%20image%20courtesy%3A%20Atik%20Bheda%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20interviews%20and%20reporting%20for%20this%20feature%20were%20conducted%20in%202024.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20do%20you%20mean%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20a%20replica%20of%20Hagrid%E2%80%99s%20house%3F%E2%80%9D%20I%20ask%20Raghav%20Kumar%20(30)%2C%20one%20half%20of%20the%20brother%20duo%20that%20has%20conceptualised%20a%20600-sq%20ft%20beauty%20in%20the%20heartland%20of%20Rishikesh%2C%20Uttarakhand.%20As%20fans%20of%20the%20seven-part%20fantasy%20series%20%E2%80%98Harry%20Potter%E2%80%99%20will%20immediately%20guess%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20referring%20to%20the%20eight-foot-tall%20giant%20Rubeus%20Hagrid%E2%80%99s%20cabin%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20The%20Forbidden%20Forest%20%E2%80%94%20an%20ominous%20wood%20filled%20with%20wizarding%20creatures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECosy%20fires%2C%20larger-than-life%20teacups%2C%20and%20a%20drooling%20boarhound%20Fang%20filled%20most%20evenings%20that%20Harry%20and%20his%20friends%20spent%20at%20Hagrid%E2%80%99s.%20I%20often%20found%20myself%20craving%20to%20be%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20wish%20might%20just%20have%20been%20answered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaghav%20and%20Ansh%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Tiny%20Farm%20Fort%E2%80%99%20is%20reminiscent%20of%20Hagrid%E2%80%99s%20abode.%20Creating%20the%2015-ft%20doppelganger%20homestay%2C%20the%20brothers%20say%2C%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20goal%20that%20backed%20their%20transition%20from%20their%20city%20life%20in%20Delhi%20to%20the%20mountains%20in%202021.%20Instead%2C%20it%20was%20a%20consequence%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20architects%2C%20Raghav%20and%20Ansh%20(27)%20were%20keen%20on%20living%20an%20%E2%80%9Cintentional%20life%20closer%20to%20nature%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20a%20dream%20they%20felt%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20achieved%20by%20being%20a%20part%20of%20modern%20corporate%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F247572%2Fmaharashtra-ecofriendly-green-architecture-domes-arches-cost-effective-sustainable-homes-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earchitectural%20projects%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20prized%20demand%20over%20sustainability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20disconnect%20between%20the%20architect%20and%20the%20labour%20involved%20in%20these%20projects.%20There%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20greenwashing%2C%E2%80%9D%20Raghav%20notes.%20Prior%20to%202021%2C%20the%20Delhi-based%20boys%20had%20their%20week%20cut%20out%20for%20them%20%E2%80%94%20weekdays%20spent%20working%20long%20hours%20and%20weekends%20trekking%20to%20North%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F9_3aPdHLQ9Y%3Fsi%3DuSBCfoXQnBlYuCgm%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seed%20for%20Tiny%20Farm%20Fort%20was%20sown%20when%2C%20after%20one%20particular%20trek%20to%20Rishikesh%20in%20December%202020%2C%20Raghav%20and%20Ansh%20found%20themselves%20wishing%20they%20could%20stay%20back%20in%20the%20mountains%20and%20not%20return%20to%20the%20monotonous%20hustle.%20And%20they%20decided%20to%20do%20just%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20completely%20bewildered%20by%20topics%20of%20gardening%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F189744%2Fbangalore-lifestyle-one-day-holiday-village-rural-pottery-green-trip-village-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20rural%20lifestyle%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20journey%20of%20building%20Tiny%20Farm%20Fort%20has%20stretched%20their%20understanding%20in%20these%20regards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20they%20invite%20us%20into%20their%20home.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ftiny-farm-fort-sustainable-home-1721812338.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tiny%20Farm%20Fort%20is%20a%20sustainably%20built%20homestay%20in%20Rishikesh%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ftiny-farm-fort-sustainable-home-1721812338.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ftiny-farm-fort-sustainable-home-1721812338-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ftiny-farm-fort-sustainable-home-1721812338-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ftiny-farm-fort-sustainable-home-1721812338-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ftiny-farm-fort-sustainable-home-1721812338-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358212%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETiny%20Farm%20Fort%20is%20a%20sustainably%20built%20homestay%20